rmal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(244,245,246); FONT-VARIANT: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">Ho&aacute;</strong></strong></strong></td>\r\n			<td align="center" class="Normal" width="192">\r\n				<strong style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(244,245,246); FONT-VARIANT: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(244,245,246); FONT-VARIANT: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(244,245,246); FONT-VARIANT: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">Tiếng Anh</strong></strong></strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="right" class="Normal">\r\n	<strong style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; W